text: Richard Henry Bagnall-Oakeley was an archer from Great Britain. He was born on 12 November 1865 and died on 5 July 1947. Bagnall-Oakeley competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Richard Bagnall-Oakeley == References == Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain Category:1865 births Category:1947 deaths
